ygData.messageBody:
I am based in Qeynos.

As a human, you might be able to visit the Dark Elf city if your faction is low enough. But as for the Troll city, I doubt so ;-) Ne ways, you will start puking once you enter due to the foul smell and those ugly female trolls. Darn, wait til you see a naked female orge! Lah Gi Best siah!

Shees, the other day I managed to wake up at 12 midnight and gamed til 6am. Damn tired but that was all i could play for the whole week. What time do your log on?

Wilson
